4. Release Impact Analysis
Where: Change & Drift, Workload Operations What: When a DBA annotates a release window (e.g., "Deploy v2.4 at 2pm UTC"), OVERWATCH automatically compares the 4-hour window before and after the release for:

Query duration regression by query signature hash
