The Pattern That Gets You to 99
The common thread across all these features is shifting from reactive display to proactive intelligence:

Current state (93): "Here is what happened. Here is where to look."
Target state (99): "Here is what happened, here is why, here is what will happen next, and here is what to do about it — verified automatically after you act."
The dashboard that tells you something is wrong before you open it, explains why with AI-grounded evidence, predicts when it will get worse, suggests the fix with generated SQL, executes the fix with your permission, and verifies the outcome 7 days later — that's a 99.
